<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.2">
<l>eḷivaru miyalviṉa ṉilaivaram pilapala piṟappā</l>
<l>yoḷivaru muḻunala mutalila kēṭila vīṭān</l>
<l>teḷitaru nilaimaiya toḻivilaṉ muḻuvatu miṟaiyō</l>
<l>ṉaḷivaru maruḷiṉō ṭakattaṉaṉ puṟattaṉa ṉamaintē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is of a nature easy [and] difficult. Being in many births, without limits of position,</l>
<l>he is the whole effulgent goodness, liberation without beginning, without end.</l>
<l>He is without an end that would be of a quality that is understood, the lord of the whole,</l>
<l>suited to be the one inside [and] outside, with a grace that is nourishing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
